    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't have insurance for the clinic right now and it's a long trip to get there. if i take a double dose of antihistamine like 20mg instead of 10mg, will that work faster to open up my chest? i really just want to sleep this off and stop the whistling.",
